Package org.apache.taverna.server.master.common

This package contains the common XML elements used throughout Taverna Server's various interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Namespaces
    A convenient place to keep the names of URIs so that they can be got right once.
    Roles
    The roles defined in this webapp.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Capability
    Describes a single capability supported by Taverna Server's workflow execution core.
    Credential
    A description of a private credential.
    Credential.Dummy
    A credential that is just used for deleting credentials by ID.
    Credential.KeyPair
    A description of a credential that is a public/private key-pair in some kind of key store.
    Credential.Password
    A description of a credential that is a username and password.
    DirEntryReference
    A reference to something that is in a directory below the working directory of a workflow run, described using JAXB.
    DirEntryReference.DirectoryReference
    A reference to a directory, done with JAXB.
    DirEntryReference.FileReference
    A reference to a file, done with JAXB.
    InputDescription
    A description of the inputs to a workflow, described using JAXB.
    InputDescription.Port
    The type of a single port description.
    ProfileList
    Description of the profiles that can apply to a workflow.
    ProfileList.Info
    Description of a single workflow profile.
    RunReference
    A reference to a single workflow run, described using JAXB.
    Trust
    A description of a trusted identity or identities.
    Uri
    A class that makes it simpler to work with an element with a URI in an href attribute.
    Uri.Rewriter
    A bean that allows configuration of how to rewrite generated URIs to be secure.
    VersionedElement
    The type of an element that declares the version of the server that produced it.
    Workflow
    Encapsulation of a T2flow or Scufl2 document.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Permission
    Description of a permission to access a particular workflow run.
    Status
    States of a workflow run.
    Workflow.ContentType  

Package org.apache.taverna.server.master.common Description

This package contains the common XML elements used throughout Taverna Server's various interfaces.
